               <code code="51945-4" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="PACKAGE LABEL.PRINCIPAL DISPLAY PANEL"/>
               <title>AIR, COMPRESSED
(MEDICAL AIR, USP)</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <br/>AIR, COMPRESSED   UN1002  (MEDICAL AIR, USP)   NON-FLAMMABLE GAS 2     37638  (02/05)</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>WARNING: For breathing support when used by properly trained personnel. For medical applications, Rx only.<br/>Administration of medical air may be hazardous or contraindicated. For medical use only by or under the supervision <br/>of a licensed practitioner who is experienced in the use and administration of medical air and is familiar with<br/> the indications, effects, dosages, methods, and frequency and duration of administration, and with the hazards,<br/>contraindications, and side effects and the precautions to be taken. CAUTION: HIGH PRESSURE GAS. MAY ACCELERATE COMBUSTION. Keep oil and grease away. Use equipment rated for cylinder pressure. Cylinder temperature should not exceed <br/>52 degrees C (125 degrees F). Close valve after each use and when empty. Use a back flow preventive device in the piping. Use in accordance with the Material Safety Data Sheet (MSDS).</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>CAS: 132259-10-0                                           DO NOT REMOVE THIS PRODUCT LABEL</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Vagabond Welding Supply<br/>
                     <br/>55870 Yucca Trail Yucca Valley, CA 92284  (760) 365-3070</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="Vagabondhpairsl"/>
                  </paragraph>
